abstract: Corinna da Fonseca-Wollheim reviews performance by International Contemporary Ensemble at Abrons Arts Center.
lead_paragraph: The International Contemporary Ensemble brought “Untempered,” a program full of unusual tunings, to Abrons Arts Center.
